mrm:ReviewPetLicenseApplication
      rdf:type mrm:Process ;
      rdfs:subClassOf mrm:Active ;
      dcterms:description """Review Application, Verify and Collect Supporting
Documents.

The Agent will review the application and collect and verify supporting documents. Copies of the microchip or spay/neuter information is no longer being tracked. Once it is entered into MAP, it is considered to have been seen and approved by the agent.. The agents just attaches the documentation to the financial statement and it is sent with the rest of the payment to Finance. It is not looked at again.""" ;
      dcterms:title "Review Pet License Application" .

